c: 66
v: 8
t: "A wid iumnen! Utubet ﾃ貌bbi, ppuba n ﾃｻﾃｻeﾃｪ! Ahat Mass nnwen ad awen Ikkes tucmitin nnwen, u a kwen Issekcem ar Loennet, ddaw as isaffen ppazzalen. Assen, ﾃ貌bbi ur Isdullu Nnbi akked wid iumnen yides. Tafat nnsen teppeddu zdat sen, u yeffus nnsen. Ad qqaﾃｴen: \"a Mass nne$! Tim ane$ tafat nne$, Semmeﾃｪ ane$; ih, Keﾃｧﾃｧ, Tzemrev i yal cci"